I said this last year too but more gymcel bros should consider getting into hobby shot put. It's not cardio or anything that can mess with your recovery, trains rotational strength and obliques/core, and a shot is trivially cheap to buy and you can even just throw it at the park.

It requires muscle strength so it's similar to weightlifting and you already have the mass base. I guess discus throw and hammer throw are also similar, but it's probably a bit easier to accidentally decapitate someone if you're doing it outside and not at a stadium or something.
